- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper deals with factorizations of pseudowords, which can be seen as a type of data structure. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as the paper involves the study of information encoded in pseudowords and labeled linear orders. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is a possibility as the paper involves the study of the relationship between pseudowords and labeled linear orders, which can be seen as a logical relationship.
